Dialogs.Dialog: Hey... Have you ever seen a donut shop that sells wagons?
My friend said that the other day I bought it and ate it and it was really delicious.
There are many other delicious donut shops, right?
That's right, but... I definitely like those donuts! That's what I was told.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲Do you like it? I'm curious...
I was also curious. But it looks like it's a mobile sales store... I can't find it at all.
Really? Thank you, if you find it, let's eat together♪
(Oh, is that a rumored donut shop?)

What is the promise... what is it?
Wow♪ Did you remember it properly? I'm happy.
I choose the kinds of foods so eat whatever I like.
Really, please feel free to come♪
●I chose the one that ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ likes... what do you think?
……delicious! Are you okay. It seems like you know my taste very well ▼

What is that? ...Oh, yeah, my friend said he had found a delicious crepe shop.

Ah, I'd love to try the crepes from that restaurant too.
So, let's look for ● as well.
(Oh, is that a crepe shop that's the rumored crepe shop?)

Haha...I wonder if that's what happens to be dumplings rather than flowers?
Anyway, let's go buy it soon.
If you don't feel this crisp, it'll become even more slender, right?
I want to eat something cold...

I don't know, where is it?
They are sold on mobile wagons, so it seems they don't know when and where they are. That kind of thing makes me even more interested.
Well, if you see me, I'll contact you. Let's eat together♪
Understood. ●I'll contact you if I see them too.
(Oh, is that a rumored gelato shop?)
▲主人公＊▲. Did you find a gelato shop?
It's a cuter shop than I thought. It makes me feel happy somehow.
I have to get excited and not eat too much.
I only eat one more. But would you be happy if you could give me a taste of yours too?
I once talked about my friend about autumn flavors. But I thought everyone was different and there were a lot.
Yeah. Hey, what do you think of autumn flavors?
●These are... saury, matsutake mushrooms, persimmons, chestnuts...
Yes, that's it! I was reminded of chestnuts.
That's good, chestnut. Come to think of it, it seems like they've been selling sweet chestnuts recently.
Oh, I've heard of it. But I don't know when and where I'm.
Hmm, I might look for it...
(Oh, is that a rumoured sweet chestnut shop?)
Yes, I don't mind at all.
There was something I wanted to give to ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, so I hurriedly brought it.
Autumn taste. I thought I'd like to eat together.
I'm so happy, I can't help but remember you. I wonder if I'll give you a treat... haha ​​▼
When I was a child...Did you not have to have a bonfire and have them grilled sweet potatoes?
Ah, maybe that was the case.
The roasted potatoes wrapped in foil were hot and almost burned. But it was sweet and fragrant...it was tasty.
I haven't seen such a scene recently... On the contrary, I might not have heard much about the roasted sweet potato shops...
Ah, when you say it... I'm sure there's somewhere.
Is he really there? Ah...I'm starting to want to eat grilled sweet potatoes.
●Other. I think I'll buy it next time I see it.
So, please do my best too? Hehe♪
(Oh, is that a rumored baked sweet potato shop?)
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, I bought the same one.
It's a grilled sweet potato from a roasted sweet potato shop. here you are
I just want to taste the nostalgic taste of my childhood.
So, I have to check it out.
Hey, do you believe that you are a UFO?
Well... I think UFOs are the fact that it's not possible to say that.
I see. So if I said I saw a UFO, would you believe me?
Yes. Actually, my friend saw it. I even took a picture of that kid. They say, "I've been coming here a lot lately, so everyone can take pictures."
Wow... But if you can really see it, you might want to see ● as well.
me too. Yes, I'll let you know if you find it.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, have you seen UFO since then?
Well, my heart is proud. Did you see a UFO?
Actually, that's true. Look, this is a photo of the evidence.
Liar, really? ...No!? Something's in the picture!
So that's the UFO that ● saw.
Amazing! Can I copy this? I have to show it to my friends too!
Um, do you know that ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is Twassy?
Twissy? Um... that's right, isn't it? A giant creature that is rumored to live in Lake Tobano.
What, do you know after all? ●I recently learned about it.
I think this is a pretty famous story around here. Many people have seen it.
Hmm, I want to believe that there is, but when I think about why no one can capture a definitive video...hey?
If you bring a photo, I'll believe it...hehe♪
Actually, I took a great photo!
Hehe, I'm excited. That's a really amazing photo, isn't it?
It's a big scoop! Come on, do you know what this is?
Yes, Twissy! ●I looked at it with my own eyes!
Amazing, amazing! Twissy was there after all. I definitely believe it!

ah. Have a lot of fun!

picture? ●? I haven't said anything though.
